        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/morrison-cou2-sqa",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 5 CFD code",
        "description": "The CFD solver must be under version control with documented release notes, a full regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes, and traceability from source code to executable. All test cases must pass at the released version used for production runs."
      },
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is managed under Git version control with tagged releases. A 214-case regression suite covering turbulent pipe, rotating disk, and blood-analogue channel flows was executed at the tagged release; all cases passed within tolerance. Build reproducibility was confirmed via containerised Docker image with SHA-256 digest pinned in the simulation manifest."
    },
    {
